edia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spain's Sergio de Celis Montalban won the heat in 48.49, with Israel's Tomer Frankel second in 48.66.\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 418, \"end\": 423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.985593111392341, \"rank\": 0.014599047588132453, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 442, \"end\": 451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rodriguez,_Rizal\", \"score\": 0.9954622884567246, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Montalban\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rodriguez,_Rizal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rodriguez,_Rizal\"}, {\"begin\": 480, \"end\": 486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999114154959957, \"rank\": 8.859233073231498e-05, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carter was the first TT athlete to qualify for the Paris games.\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 521, \"end\": 527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"score\": 0.9994633244775133, \"rank\": 0.0005106879885172033, \"text\": \"Carter\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Carter\"}, {\"begin\": 542, \"end\": 544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isle_of_Man_TT\", \"score\": 0.9961342472055902, \"rank\": 0.002943219956303289, \"text\": \"TT\", \"types\": [], \"wiki